metadata.name: Commemorative APEcoin #1
metadata.description: Commemorative APEcoin ($COMAPE) are coins that were traded for 1 $APE for 1 $COMAPE so that I can buy a MAYC. A Token of Gratitiude, however what is special about these coins are not only the 10k limited supply but they were minted from the past, present and future with different minted years on every coin. They seem to defy time itself!
